content.article_body: ISLAMABAD, Jul 24 (APP):The Senate session commenced on Thursday at the Parliament House with Senate Chairman Syed Yousaf Raza Gilani in the chair, as part of the ongoing 352nd session of the Upper House. The session commenced at 5:15 PM and included the presentation of legislative business, calling attention notices, and matters of public importance.
